title: Sleek & Modern, Pet Friendly 2BED/1BATH
posting_body: ['ADDRESS: 348-B SAN PABLO AVE.', 'MILLBRAE, CA 94030', 'Step inside to be captivated by a sleek and modern, new 2BED/1BATH accessory dwelling unit.', 'Dazzling with tons of natural light and vaulted ceilings.', 'All new appliances including washer and dryer, and smart home features make for easy living.', 'Situated for busy days and leisurely evenings, this ideal location is perfect for those who appreciate the convenience.', "Minutes from Starbucks, Trader Joe's Millbrae BART, HWY 101, and more.", 'CONTACT US', 'TO VIEW', 'Call/Text/Email', 'ADDITIONAL FEATURES', '• Minimalist Design', '• Vaulted Ceilings', '• Dishwasher', '• Washer and Dryer In Unit', '• Smart Google Home Equipped', 'PARKING', '• Street parking', 'LOCATION', '• Easy Access to Shopping and Restaurants', '• Incredible commute access to Millbrae BART', '• SFO International Airport, HWY 101/280/380', 'LEASING TERMS', '• Rent: $2,600', '• Deposit: $3,900', '• 1-Year Lease Required', '• Renters Insurance Required', '•', 'No Smoking', 'UTILITIES', '• Utilities Not Included', '• Landscaping Included', 'PET TERMS', '• Additional Pet Rent $35 per pet, per month', '• Additional Pet Deposit $500', '• Max 2 pet(s); Max weight 35lbs', 'For pet and animal details visit:', '<URL>', 'VISIT OUR WEBSITE TO VIEW RESIDENT QUALIFYING CRITERIA AND TO APPLY RIGHT AWAY ONLINE!', 'Each resident over the age of 18 must submit a separate rental application.', "You’ll need to provide your contact information, where you've lived, who will be residing with you, income, and other personal information.", 'Application Fee: $40 per person', 'Pet Application: $25 per pet', 'Professionally Managed By Rockaway Residential Management', '<URL>', 'show contact info', 'DRE #02078912', 'Information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed.', 'Square Footage is Approximate.']
